subject: Beach Volleyball
lead_paragraph: Misty May-Treanor will return next weekend to the beach volleyball tour in Glendale, Ariz., and be reunited with Kerri Walsh, her partner for two Olympic gold medals. It will be their first competition together in 2009. Walsh sat out most of the season after having a baby in the spring, but returned last month.
